r-3842457">明年夏天</a>”为特色。 </p><figure id="attachment_3842469" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3842469" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3842469" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/damiano-david-pool-rovaris-trucillo-1.jpg" alt="达米亚诺·戴维（Damiano David）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/damiano-david-pool-rovaris-trucillo-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/damiano-david-pool-rovaris-trucillo-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/damiano-david-pool-rovaris-trucillo-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/damiano-david-pool-rovaris-trucillo-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/damiano-david-pool-rovaris-trucillo-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/damiano-david-pool-rovaris-trucillo-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3842469" class="wp-caption-text">达米亚诺·戴维（Damiano David）。学分：Rovaris Trucillo/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> David此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maneskin-damiano-david-inteview-silverlines-solo-album-band-future-3797604" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在与<em>NME</em>谈到专辑时</a>，他分享道：“我会说，这将非常过分，非常戏剧性，非常戏剧性。这绝对是个人的。这是关于活着的戏剧；尤其是在这种情况下。”</p><p>同时，Sparks最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sparks-repeat-their-mantra-since-1972-on-single-do-things-my-own-way-announce-new-album-mad-with-uk-europe-and-japan-tour-3833179">宣布了他们的第28张录音室专辑“ Mad！”</a> ，将于5月23日通过侵犯记录（<a href="https://transgressive.lnk.to/mad" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处预订/预保留</a>）发布。到目前为止，他们已经分享了单曲“ Jansport背包”和“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sparks-repeat-their-mantra-since-1972-on-single-do-things-my-own-way-announce-new-album-mad-with-uk-europe-and-japan-tour-3833179">我自己的方式做事</a>”。</p><p> &#39;疯狂的！&#39;是Sparks自2023年以来的第一张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sparks-the-girl-is-crying-in-her-latte-review-3446548">女孩在她的拿铁咖啡中哭泣</a>》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sparks-the-girl-is-crying-in-her-latte-review-3446548">（ <i>NME）</i>授予了四颗星星</a>，并指出：像其他乐器一样，让这首歌毫不掩饰地朝着特殊的方向移动。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bilbao-bbk-2025-damiano-david-sparks-and-more-announced-as-full-line-up-revealed-3848361">Bilbao BBK邮政2025年：达米亚诺·戴维（Damiano David），斯帕克斯（Sparks）和更多人宣布了全阵容，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
