-how-new-pal-chappell-roan-helped-her-through-bad-week-3848322">揭示了“新朋友”查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）如何帮助她度过了“糟糕的一周”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus-and-Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_WireImage-and-Swan-Gallet_WWD-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus-and-Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_WireImage-and-Swan-Gallet_WWD-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus-and-Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_WireImage-and-Swan-Gallet_WWD-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus-and-Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_WireImage-and-Swan-Gallet_WWD-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus-and-Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_WireImage-and-Swan-Gallet_WWD-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus-and-Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_WireImage-and-Swan-Gallet_WWD-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus-and-Chappell-Roan.-CREDIT_-Alberto-E.-Rodriguez_WireImage-and-Swan-Gallet_WWD-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucy-dacus">露西·达科斯（Lucy Dacus）</a>分享了她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a>的“新友谊”如何帮助她度过了糟糕的一周。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/boygenius-the-record-nme-album-of-the-year-2023-3555857">Boygenius关于“记录”的持久力量：“我们感觉就像我们希望的一样好”</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Boygenius">Boygenius</a> Singer在接受<a href="https://people.com/lucy-dacus-chappell-roan-cheered-her-up-bad-week-exclusive-11699418" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志的</em></a>新采访中透露，她和她的乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julien-baker">朱利安·贝克（Julien Baker）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">菲比·布里格斯（Phoebe Bridgers）</a>首先与罗恩（Roan）建立了恋爱关系，因为她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-chastises-fans-weird-and-creepy-behaviour-thats-not-normal-3785060">公开谈论了一些粉丝的“怪异”和“令人毛骨悚然的行为</a>。</p><p>达科斯说：“当[Chappell]感到非常稀薄时，Boygenius中的所有人都在鼓励她，并告诉她这将消失，这只是一次非常旋转的旅行，当每个人都有话要说时，” Dacus说。</p><p>她继续分享罗恩（Roan）返回了支持，并解释说：“几周前我有一个糟糕的一周，在那儿，让音乐变得更糟，这让我想知道我是否应该跳过生活的一部分，在我的生活中，我的生活中没有我的名字，”“谈话”歌手大笑。 “而且她就像，&#39;不，您所做的很重要，并使很多人感到孤独。&#39;”</p><p> Dacus补充说“好运，宝贝！”歌手还送了她的鲜花。 “我很高兴能以如此良好的心为新朋友。” </p><figure id="attachment_3841348" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841348" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841348" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841348" class="wp-caption-text">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）。学分：录音学院的丽贝卡·萨普/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>达克斯说，她和罗恩都“相互”学习，“当人们恨你时，他们就不认识你。”</p><p> “另一方面，当他们爱你时，他们也不认识你，”达科斯指出。 “因此，这就像保护自己免受仇恨的侵害，但也不要让其他人的爱取代您生活中真正的爱。</p><p>她补充说：“他们可能会了解您，但他们真的不知道您是一个人。”</p><p>评论是在Dacus的第四张录音室专辑“ Forever Is A Fene”中的促销活动，该专辑定于3月28日通过Polydor/Geffen（<a href="https://lucydacus.lnk.to/foreverisafeeling" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预播</a>）发行。</p><p>到目前为止，LP的四张单曲已分享：“<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lucy-dacus-vulnerable-new-single-talk-3846027">谈话”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lucy-dacus-new-album-forever-is-a-feeling-two-powerful-singles-us-tour-3829267">“脚踝”和“灰色”（两者都在一月份到达</a>）以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lucy-dacus-shares-new-anthem-for-queer-tenderness-best-guess-and-announces-2025-uk-and-european-tour-listen-buy-tickets-3837051">上个月的“最佳猜测”</a> 。她最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lucy-dacus-reveals-tracklist-for-upcoming-album-forever-is-a-feeling-3845201#">透露了“永远的感觉”的13首曲目列表</a>，其中包括妮可·雅克琳·史密斯（Nicole Jaclyn Smith）的定制插图。</p><p>在尚未听到的剩下的10条曲目中，有专辑揭幕战&#39;Calliope Prelude&#39;，&#39;Modigliani&#39;，标题曲目“ Forever是一种感觉”，“最想要的人”和“迷失的时间”。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hozier">Hozier</a>还将出现在专辑中，即曲目“ Bullseye”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3846036" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3846036" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3846036" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez.jpg" alt="露西·达克斯（Lucy Dacus）。学分：Shervin Lainez" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Lucy-Dacus.-Credit-Shervin-Lainez-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" 